# Extraordinary Equipment

This document is intended to provide new item options for the WC5E project, ranging from altered prices for existing items due to the increased technological prowess of the races of Azeroth, to new mechanical equipment that relies more on scientific knowledge than magical enhancements, to new magical items found throughout the Warcraft setting, up to powerful artifacts.

This document is still very much a work in progress, with new items being added constantly as I come across new items that I feel should make their way into the setting. 

