# New Equipment

<style> .phb#NewWeapons:after { display:none; } </style>
## New Weapons

<div class='classTable wide'>

##### New Weapons
Name|Cost|Damage|Weight|Properties
---|---|---|---|---
Blunderbuss of Khaz Modan|100 gp|3d4 piercing|12 lb.|Ammunition (range 30/45), heavy, scattershot (1d8), special, two-handed
Dwarven Fishing Pole|80 gp|3d4 piercing|4 lb.|Ammunition (range 10/15), scattershot (3d4), two-handed
Gnomish Net-o-Matic Projector|25 gp|--|5 lb.|Ammunition (range 80/320), loading, special, two-handed
Grappling Hook Launcher|??|??|??|??
Harpoon Gun|70 gp|1d6 piercing|15 lb.|Ammunition (range 25/100), loading, heavy, special, two-handed
Sniper Rifle|150 gp|3d6 piercing|6 lb.|Ammunition (range 150/600), heavy, special, two-handed
