\pagebreakNum

#### Gnomish Alarm-o-Bot
*Wondrous item, uncommon*

A gnomish alarm-o-bot must be prepared, keying it to respond to your voice. This process takes 10 minutes. After it has been prepped, activating an alarm-o-bot is an action and it remains active for up to 24 hours or until it drops to 0 hit points. You can break the duration of operation up into 10 minute increments. 

It is friendly to you and your companions. You can use a bonus action to command how the creature moves and what action it takes on its next turn, or to give it general orders, such as to attack your enemies. In absence of orders, it stands in place and actively searches for creatures.

#### Gnomish Battle Chicken
*Wondrous item, uncommon*

A gnomish battle chicken must be prepared, keying it to respond to your voice. This process takes 10 minutes. After it has been prepped, activating a battle chicken is an action and it remains active for up to 8 hours or until it drops to 0 hit points. You can break the duration of operation up into 10 minute increments. 

It is friendly to you and your companions. You can use a bonus action to command how the chicken moves and what action it takes on its next turn, or to give it general orders, such as to attack your enemies. In absence of orders, it acts as a chicken would.

___
