#### Skullflame Shield
[Todo. When struck in combat, 1% chance to deal fire damage to adjacent creatures, 3% chance to steal life from attacker.]

#### The Immovable Object
<img src='https://gamepedia.cursecdn.com/wowpedia/a/a8/The_Immovable_Object.JPG?version=d5e858c1494c052621b17354fd62353b' style='325px' />

*Shield (tower), rare (requires attunement)*

While you wear this shield, you have advantage on saving throws versus any effect that would move your character. 

As an action you can speak the command word and affix the shield in place as though it were an *immovable rod*. If you are wearing the shield while it is in this form, you lose the shield's bonus to Armor Class but you are immune to any effect that moves your character. You can speak the command word again to end the effect.

If this shield ever touches the magic item *the unstoppable force*, both items are immediately destroyed.

#### Thistefur Hide
*Armor (hide), uncommon*

Made from the hides of thistlefur furbolgs. Whenever an enemy damages you with a melee attack, they take 1d4 piercing damage.

