#### Spider Ring
*Ring, uncommon (requires attunement)*

While you wear this ring, you ignore movement restrictions caused by webbing and while in contact with a web you know the exact location of each other creature in contact with the same web.

The ring also has 3 charges. It regains 1d3 charges at dusk. You can expend 1 charge to cast the *spider climb* or *web* spells.

