## Rods
#### Dartol's Rod
*Rod, very rare (requires attunement)*

This steel rod is adorned with feathers and a furbolg skull. You can use its power to *polymorph*, as the spell, into a furbolg. This effect requires no concentration and lasts until you transform back. 

While you are polymorphed, other furbolg are considered charmed by you (no save). Attacking them breaks this effect. You can also cast *suggestion* at will, but only on furbolgs.

