#### Scroll of Greater Ability
*Scroll, rarity varies* 

Each *scroll of greater ability* works on a single ability score, depending on the type of scroll.

##### Scroll of Greater Ability
Ability Score|Rarity
---|---
Charisma|Uncommon
Constitution|Rare
Dexterity|Rare
Intelligence|Uncommon
Strength|Uncommon
Wisdom|Rare

Using an action to read the scroll causes one of your ability scores, dependent on the type of scroll, to be increased to 19 for 24 hours. The scroll has no effect if your ability score is already 19 or higher. 

Once the scroll has been used, the words on it fade and it crumbles into dust.

