#### Fandral's Flamescythe
*Staff, rare (requires attunement by a druid)*

This staff has a red gem glowing with contained flame set on the head, around which a large metal design slowly rotates. Attacks with this staff deal an additional 1d10 fire damage.

Additionally, when you use your shapeshift ability, you can choose to transform into an animal composed of flame. You retain all the normal effects of your form and you gain the following:
- You have immunity to fire damage.
- Your attacks deal an additional 1d10 fire damage.
- You have the Fire Form, Illumination, and Water Susceptibility abilities of a fire elemental. 
