[Todo. Associated with the keeper of the Life sphere of influence.] This is a long staff with a gold head piece. In the center of the head is a green gem of some unknown mineral that allows light to shine through. The staff is warm to the touch and if left too long in one place, plants turn to face it as if facing the sun.

#### Staff of the Arcane
*Staff, very rare (requires attunement by a mage)*

You have resistance to force damage while you hold this staff.

The staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC: *arcane explosion* ^WHH^ (3 charges), *mage armor* (1 charge), *magic missile* (1 charge), or *polymorph* (4 charges).

The staff regains 1d6 + 4 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff lets out the sound of a bleating sheep and then disappears like a popping soap bubble.

#### Staff of Conjuring
[Todo. Can be used to conjure muffins.]

#### Staff of Curses
*Staff, very rare (requires attunement by a warlock)*

You have resistance to force damage while you hold this staff.

The staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC: *bestow curse* (3 charges), *hex* (1 charge), *remove curse* (3 charges), or *toll the dead* (0 charges, damage as a cantrip of your warlock level).

The staff regains 1d6 + 4 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff lets out an unearthly scream of anguish that can be heard for 300 feet before crumbling into white ash.

