#### Staff of the Waves
*Staff, very rare (requires attunement by a druid or shaman)*

While you hold this staff, you have a swim speed equal to your movement speed and can breathe underwater.

The staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC: *control water* (4 charges), *create or destroy water* (1 charge), *maelstrom* ^XGE^ (5 charges), *tidal wave* ^XGE^ (3 charges), or *water walk* (3 charges).

The staff regains 1d6 + 4 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff turns to water and is destroyed.

#### Staff of the Winds
*Staff, very rare (requires attunement by a druid or shaman)*

You have resistance to lightning and thunder damage while you hold this staff.

The staff has 10 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 or more of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC: *call lightning* (3 charges), *control winds* ^XGE^ (5 charges), *feather fall* (1 charge), *gust of wind* (2 charges), or *thunderwave* (1 charge).

The staff regains 1d6 + 4 expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, the staff crumbles into dust which is carried away by a gust of wind, and is destroyed.

