#### Blight
[Todo. Polearm. Diseases target for X damage and another X damage over 10 sec.] This long-handled halberd has a narrow, razor-sharp blade and wickedly barbed tip that bears a faintly glowing, sickly green aura. The shaft is wrapped in dried skin peeled from the corpses of zombies. The faint odor of rotting eggs surrounds the wielder in combat. These nasty-looking and nasty-smelling items are not a favorite among the living for obvious reasons.

