#### Starshatter
*Weapon (any sword), very rare (requires attunement by a spellcaster)*

You gain a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.

This sword has a line of eight crystals laid out along the blade, glowing like a constellation. Each crystal corresponds to a charge; when the charge is expended, a crystal fades and becomes dull. You can expend a charge from this weapon as a bonus action to cast the *blinding smite* spell (DC 15).

The sword regains 1d6 + 2 charges at first starlight. If the last charge is expended, roll a d20. On a 1, the sword permanently loses all charges but retains its bonus to attack and damage rolls.

