#### Sul'thraze the Lasher
*Weapon (greatsword), very rare (requires attunement)*

You gain a +2 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon. You can separate Sul'thraze the Thrasher into the twin swords, Jang'thraze the Protector and Sang'thraze the Deflector as an action. 

When you hit a creature with this weapon, the target must make a DC 15 Constitution saving throw. On a failure, they are cursed for 1 minute. While cursed, whenever they deal damage with a melee attack they must reroll the damage and take the lower total. Additionally, they take an additional 1d4 necrotic damage whenever they are dealt damage.

