#### Weapon of Returning
*Weapon (weapon with thrown property), uncommon (requires attunement)*

An enchantment most often seen on kaldorei moonglaives. When you throw a weapon of returning, the weapon returns to your hand after it hits or misses its target. It does so after the attack roll resolves, allowing you to make as many attacks as you can normally make with the Attack action.

