#### Wolfslayer's Rifle
*Weapon (double musket), very rare*

This complex weapon has two barrels and a rotating cylinder that contains extra shots. It also comes equipped with a scope and a bayonet. You can fire this weapon up to 12 times before needing to reload. 

Optionally, you can fire two shots at once provided you have at least two shots left, though firing in this way jostles your aim more than usual. When you use this option, you make two attack rolls against the same target, with a -2 penalty on both attack rolls.

