## Wondrous Items
#### Abyss Shard
[Todo. Warlock item. Allows summoning of voidwalker w/o spell slots or soul shards.]

#### Alchemist's Stone
*Wondrous item, very rare (requires attunement)*

While attuned to this glowing yellow gem, your Strength, Dexterity, Constitution, Intelligence, Wisdom, and Charisma are increased by 1. As normal, this cannot bring your stats above 20. Additionally, when you imbibe a potion that has dice rolled for numerical effects, such as the number of hit points restored in the case of a potion of healing, you can roll the dice twice and take either result.

When attuned to this item and using alchemist's supplies to craft items, crafting the item takes half the normal amount of time.

