#### Bag of Treats
*Wondrous item, common*

This belt pouch appears empty and has 10 charges. While holding the pouch, you can use an action to expend 1 of its charges, speak the name of a type of beast, and pull out a small biscuit flavored and scented to appeal to that creature. You have advantage on Charisma checks involving beasts with a CR of 1 or less when you use this biscuit. The pouch regains 1d6 + 4 expended charges at dawn.

#### Banner(s) of X
