You can also use this book to cast the spell *animate dead*. Once the book has been used to cast the spell, it cannot be used again for 24 hours. Any undead raised by use of this book are under the control of whoever is attuned to it. If you lose attunement to this item, any undead raised by it will immediately attack you.

