#### Chromie's Spare Pocketwatch
*Wondrous item, very rare (requires attunement)*

This bronze pocketwatch keeps perfect time, even under the most unusual circumstances. It tends to store excess bits of time in itself, allowing a user to release it for their benefit. You can click a button on the side of the watch to gain the benefits of *haste* (no concentration required). You can use this for one minute, either all at once or in one round increments. Clicking the button to start the haste effect is a bonus action, and ending it does not cost an action. You are not incapacitated when the duration ends. The watch regains one round of *haste* for every 4 hours it is not used.

