#### Drums of Battle
*Wondrous item, uncommon*

These large kodo leather drums have 7 charges. They regain 1d6 + 1 charges at dawn. When the last charge is expended, roll a d20. On a 1, the leather splits in half and the item becomes nonmagical.

You can bang against this drum and expend a charge to cast the *heroism* spell on a creature within 30 feet. For every extra charge you expend while using the drums, you can affect an extra creature.

#### Drums of Panic
*Wondrous item, uncommon*

These large kodo leather drums have 7 charges. They regain 1d6 + 1 charges at dawn. When the last charge is expended, roll a d20. On a 1, the leather splits in half and the item becomes nonmagical.

You can bang against this drum and expend a charge to use the *cause fear* spell (DC 13). You cast it as a 1st level spell; for every extra charge you expend while using the drums, you increase the spell level by 1.

#### Drums of Restoration
