#### Hearthstone
*Wondrous item, very rare*

When you focus on this fist sized stone for 10 minutes, you can use it to cast the *word of recall* spell. In order to use the spell to teleport, you must first use the spell to set a designated location. The location must be one that you are currently in, and have spent at least 8 hours a day for the last 30 days within 50 feet of that location, and not been in danger while doing so. Most often this is a person's home, hence the name of the stone. 

Once you use the stone, you cannot use it again for 7 days. A newly found stone is not attuned to a specific location.

