# Legendary Weapons of Azeroth

This section is dedicated to the most iconic and difficult to obtain legendary and near-legendary items in WoW. It will be its own section in the final document, showcasing the history and lore of the item as well as a proper image for each. For now, only the list of items and their properties will be posted.
 
The items that make it to this particular list are those that have a Legacy or Feat of Strength achievement associated with them.


Item|Achievement
---|---
[Atiesh, Greatstaff of the Guardian](https://wow.gamepedia.com/Atiesh,_Greatstaff_of_the_Guardian) | [Atish, Greatstaff of the Guardian](https://wow.gamepedia.com/Atiesh,_Greatstaff_of_the_Guardian_(achievement))
[Benediction](https://wow.gamepedia.com/Benediction)/[Anathema](https://wow.gamepedia.com/Anathema) | [The Balance of Light and Shadow](https://wow.gamepedia.com/The_Balance_of_Light_and_Shadow)
