[Rhok'delar, Longbow of the Ancient Keepers](https://wow.gamepedia.com/Rhok%27delar,_Longbow_of_the_Ancient_Keepers)/[Lok'delar, Greatstaff of the Ancient Keepers](https://wow.gamepedia.com/Lok%27delar,_Stave_of_the_Ancient_Keepers) | [The Ancient Keeper](https://wow.gamepedia.com/The_Ancient_Keeper)
