# Heirloom Artifacts
___
[TODO: Artifacts that level up with you. Have upgrade levels: common at lvl 1, uncommon at lvl 5, rare at lvl 9, very rare at lvl 13, legendary at lvl 17, artifact at lvl 20. Can only be used by mono-class characters of a specific subclass.]

Alternate names for levels:
- ***Dormant.*** The state that the item is when found by random people.
- ***Awakened.*** The state that the item is in when attuned to by an appropriate class who is at least level 5. Uncommon level.
- ***Invigorated.*** Rare level, level 9.
- ***Empowered.*** Very rare level, level 13.
- ***Unshackled.*** Legendary level, level 17.
- ***Exalted.*** Artifact level, level 20 character.

